{
  "script_id": "exponential-log",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "有一种增长快得惊人，一张纸对折二十次，厚度就能超过一百米。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "这背后是指数函数，每一步都在成倍地放大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.94,
      "size": 47088,
      "text": "而它还有一个形影不离的伙伴，叫做对数，专门用来把这种疯狂增长拉回人类的尺度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "exp-concept",
      "line_id": "exp-1",
      "filename": "exp-concept-exp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/exp-concept-exp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "指数函数写作 y 等于 a 的 x 次方，这里的 a 叫底数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "exp-concept",
      "line_id": "exp-2",
      "filename": "exp-concept-exp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/exp-concept-exp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.86,
      "size": 45792,
      "text": "当底数大于一，x 每增加一，y 就乘上一个固定的倍数，曲线一路陡峭上扬。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "exp-concept",
      "line_id": "exp-3",
      "filename": "exp-concept-exp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/exp-concept-exp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.04,
      "size": 48672,
      "text": "如果底数小于一，比如二分之一，曲线就反过来一路衰减，这正是放射性衰变的样子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "log-concept",
      "line_id": "log-1",
      "filename": "log-concept-log-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/log-concept-log-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "对数问的是一个逆问题：底数的几次方才能得到某个数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "log-concept",
      "line_id": "log-2",
      "filename": "log-concept-log-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/log-concept-log-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.25,
      "size": 51984,
      "text": "所以对数正是指数的反函数，把它们画在一起，两条曲线关于直线 y 等于 x 完美对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "log-concept",
      "line_id": "log-3",
      "filename": "log-concept-log-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/log-concept-log-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.97,
      "size": 47520,
      "text": "这条对称轴就像一面镜子，指数曲线上的每个点，都能在对数曲线上找到镜像。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "log-concept",
      "line_id": "log-4",
      "filename": "log-concept-log-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/log-concept-log-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "换底公式告诉我们，任何底数的对数，都可以用自然对数相除来计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "切换不同的底数，看看曲线的陡峭程度如何随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "打开对称轴，盯住任意一点，感受指数与对数互为镜像的关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "指数函数刻画成倍的增长或衰减，对数则是它的逆运算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "两者关于直线 y 等于 x 对称，是一对互为反函数的孪生曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "exponential-log",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/exponential-log/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "从复利到分贝，从地震到 pH 值，它们无处不在，我们下次再见！"
    }
